The [[Ithorian Elders]] were a group of [[Ithorian/Legends|Ithorians]], said to be that [[Species/Legends|species]]' most important [[Ithorian religion|religious]] leaders. It was these Elders chose the [[High Priest/Legends|High Priest]], the [[Senator/Legends|senator]] representing [[Ithor/Legends|Ithor]], and other such duties. Thus it fell to the Elders to find a new [[Planet/Legends|planet]] for the Ithorian species to settle after the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]'s invasion of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]], during which their home planet was immolated.

